In [4]:
population_2000 = df[(df.variant=='Estimates') & (df.year==2000)].drop(columns=['variant', 'country_code', 'parent_code','year']).reset_index(drop=True)
population_2100 = df[(df.variant=='Medium variant') & (df.year==2100)].drop(columns=['variant', 'country_code', 'parent_code','year']).reset_index(drop=True)
In [5]:
population_2000['country'] = population_2000['country'].astype('str') 
population_2100['country'] = population_2100['country'].astype('str')
In [6]:
df = population_2000.merge(population_2100, on='country')
In [7]:
df = df.rename({'population_x': 'population_2000', 'population_y': 'population_2100'}, axis=1)
In [8]:
df['increased'] = (df['population_2100'] - df['population_2000']) > 0
In [9]:
df['percentage'] = df['population_2100'] / df['population_2000'] - 1

В яких країнах світу населення у 2100 році буде більшим, ніж було у 2000 році, а в яких меншим?¶

In [23]:
merged['increased_categorical'] = pd.Series(['Increased' if value else 'Decreased' for value in merged['increased'].values])
In [24]:
alt.Chart(merged).project(type='equalEarth').mark_geoshape(stroke='grey').encode(
    tooltip = alt.Tooltip('country:N'), 
    color = alt.Color("increased_categorical:N", 
                      scale=alt.Scale(range = ['#fc8d59', '#91cf60']), 
                      legend=alt.Legend(title=None)),
    opacity=alt.value(0.8),
).properties(width=900, height=500, background='#F9F9F9', padding=25)
